              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Au-foils of 22 um thickness.  After the bombardments",
                "the produced Hg was separated from the remaining Au.",
                "An irradiated Au-foil was heated in vacuum to 800",
                "centigrade and the evaporating Hg collected in 1 cm3",
                "quartz flask, which was held at the temperature of",
                "liquid nitrogen.  It was carefully checked that at",
                "least 97% of the produced Hg was transferred to the",
                "flask, which was subsequently sealed off."
              ]
            }
          ],
